<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-better-off">(be) better off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>更富裕；更好的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 (be) worse off  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The president hopes that the people will be better off when he quits than when he started. 
总统希望他离任的时候人民会比他就职时更富裕。</p><footer>2012 江苏</footer></div></div>